790:16771.name: .Button Group Variants
790:16771.description:
Button Group

A button group bunches toggleable actions together.
Button groups act like radios.

We recommend using them when there are less than 4 actions for text button groups.

When using as an icon only button group use as many as necessary and always pair with a tootip text on hover.

4117:108579.name: 🌈 Progress Circle
4117:108579.description:
Click on the layer called "measure" and Change the % value in the properties panel.
To show 100% change the style variant to "Complete"
To show values between 0 - 99% change the style to "Progress"

3173:74303.name: 🌈  Slider
3173:74303.description:
To update the dot location (or value)

1. Find the Value layer (or 1st and 2nd Dot Value layers in Range)

2. Go to the Auto Layout property on the right and adjust up (or down) the "Spacing between items" value (it's the one with the ]|[ icon)
